Debreate 0.7.12 Release Notes

This is a release to enable support for wx 3.0.

Known Bugs:
    *) Auto-Link Help only re-centers if "check" button is pressed
    *) dpkg fails if non-ASCII characters are in package name or dependencies
    *) Custom dialogs are buggy

New Features:
    *) wx 3.0 support
    *) Debreate Mimetype application/x-dbp created

Tasks:
    *) Add support for manpages
    *) Add option to open changelog
    *) Add option to build standalone installers
    *) Add option to build from source
    *) Add drag-and-drop support
